examples.en: He smoothed ointment over the cut.
Liz smoothed her skirt and sat down.
They smoothed out the map on the table.
She smoothed suntan lotion over her legs.
The wood was smoothed and trimmed to size.
He smoothed his tie and headed out the door.
The coin's date had been smoothed away over time.
She smoothed on some moisturizer before she put on her makeup.
She smoothed the mussiness of the bed.
